_:N7de2fbf94fe24809a477997615b11d62 <http://schema.org/name> "Alex Norris MP" .
_:N7de2fbf94fe24809a477997615b11d62 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Alex Norris was apppointed Minister of State at the Home Office on 6 September 2025.</p>\n\n<p>He was previously Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State at the Ministry of Housing, Communities and Local Government between 9 July 2024 and 6 September 2025.</p>\n\n<p>He has been the MP for Nottingham North and Kimberley (and its predecessor Nottingham North) since June 2017.</p>\n" .
